495
00:38:35.624 --> 00:38:38.681
Instead, he came in here,
barking like a damn dog..


496
00:38:38.891 --> 00:38:41.721
without a warrant.
- Cherie, Cherie.


497
00:38:41.925 --> 00:38:45.288
