00:43:03.758 --> 00:43:06.622
When they need somebody to throw
to wolves, that somebody's me.


556
00:43:06.824 --> 00:43:09.312
Not throwing anybody to wolves.
Norcut stays missing..


557
00:43:09.524 --> 00:43:11.251
they can't prove there was a crime.

558
00:43:12.190 --> 00:43:14.349
Something fishy here. The wife.

559
00:43:14.558 --> 00:43:16.683
The wife. Why hasn't she told
Vargas about it?


560
00:43:20.758 --> 00:43:21.917
Maybe she believes you.

561
00:43:26.124 --> 00:43:29.284
Yeah! All right, Rosie!

562
00:43:34.990 --> 00:43:36.513
Tom, you missed it.

563
00:43:38.090 --> 00:43:40.147
- Way to go, Rose.
- You missed it, man.


564
00:43:40.357 --> 00:43:42.823
You should have seen it.
She was great.


565
00:43:48.658 --> 00:43:51.021
- How about pizza?
- No, we can't.


566
00:43:51.224 --> 00:43:53.315
Can't. She's got homework.
I got work to do.


567
00:43:53.524 --> 00:43:54.547
I did my homework.

568
00:43:56.524 --> 00:43:59.684
Another time, kiddo, okay?

569
00:43:59.891 --> 00:44:02.755
- Thanks for coming, Uncle Eddie.
